    "h(D) takes only 2 distinct values: {1: 10, 2: 2}",
    "FATAL: 10 of 12 discriminants have h=1, only 2 have h=2 \u2014 any 'correlation' is really a 2-vs-10 group comparison with no statistical power",
    "The 13 CM j-invariants all have class number 1 by definition (Heegner numbers); non-maximal orders -8 and -16 are the only ones with h>1",
